<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/12/%e5%a2%a8%e6%b0%b4%e5%bf%ab%e7%94%a8%e5%ae%8c%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%9f%e6%af%8d%e8%b2%93%e7%94%9f%e5%b0%8f%e5%ad%a9%e9%a1%8f%e8%89%b2%e8%b6%8a%e4%be%86%e8%b6%8a%e6%b7%a1%e8%ae%93%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e5%80%91/">墨水快用完了？母貓生小孩顏色越來越淡讓網友們笑翻 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="2560" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-rplhB9mYF48-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-rplhB9mYF48-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-rplhB9mYF48-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-rplhB9mYF48-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-rplhB9mYF48-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-rplhB9mYF48-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-rplhB9mYF48-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=146%2C146&amp;ssl=1 146w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/the-lucky-neko-rplhB9mYF48-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>最近國外有名女子分享自家貓咪生產的趣事引起網路熱議，一隻年輕的母貓首次當媽媽，便一口氣生下了五隻小奶貓，其中最吸睛的莫過於小貓毛色越生越淺的現象，讓許多網友看完笑稱「好像印表機快要沒墨了」。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據了解，這名來自波蘭的女子在去年領養了一隻母貓後就非常上心，她幾乎無時無刻都陪伴在愛貓身邊，與貓咪建立起了深厚的情感連結，在不久前貓咪懷孕後，她便一直期待著愛貓順利生產的那一天。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="1830" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/leonsa-fVNyjet1CXY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C1830&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-225595" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/leonsa-fVNyjet1CXY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=1707&amp;ssl=1 1707w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/leonsa-fVNyjet1CXY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/leonsa-fVNyjet1CXY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1024%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/leonsa-fVNyjet1CXY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1365%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1365w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/leonsa-fVNyjet1CXY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=97%2C146&amp;ssl=1 97w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">五隻小貓的顏色從深到淺，讓網友笑稱：印表機快沒墨了<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>隨著時間流逝，這隻年輕的母貓媽媽終於生下了五隻可愛的小奶貓，牠們分別為兩隻深色藍灰小貓，以及兩隻淺色藍灰小貓，最後一隻則幾乎全白，這種顏色越來越淡的情況，彷彿生到一半墨水用盡，引來許多網友調侃。&nbsp;</p>



<p>儘管外觀顏色各異，小貓們的健康狀況都相當良好，貓媽媽也非常稱職地將小貓們照顧得很好，事件曝光後迅速引起網上熱議，網友們紛紛表示「好像在開盲盒」、「看起來墨水真的不足」、「最後一隻設計師偷懶」、「只打了白底」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/12/%e5%a2%a8%e6%b0%b4%e5%bf%ab%e7%94%a8%e5%ae%8c%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%9f%e6%af%8d%e8%b2%93%e7%94%9f%e5%b0%8f%e5%ad%a9%e9%a1%8f%e8%89%b2%e8%b6%8a%e4%be%86%e8%b6%8a%e6%b7%a1%e8%ae%93%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e5%80%91/">墨水快用完了？母貓生小孩顏色越來越淡讓網友們笑翻 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
